@startuml nav_age_to_cgw_boundary_routing_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Nav Age To CGW Boundary Routing Signal Flow\n(vehicle/nav/steering freshness -> CGW boundary status, warning path, and routing policy)

participant "Vehicle / steering health" as Veh #F4F7FB
participant "Infotainment / nav context" as Nav #E8F0FE
participant "CGW\nboundary and routing owner" as CGW #E8F7E8
participant "CoreState / fail-safe buses" as CoreBus #FFF4CC
participant "Gateway / diag consumers" as Consumers #FFF4CC

== Boundary Inputs ==

Veh -> CGW : frmVehicleStateCanMsg\nfrmSteeringStateCanMsg\nfrmChassisHealthMsg
Nav -> CGW : frmInfotainmentHealthMsg\nfrmNavigationRouteMsg
activate CGW
CGW -> CGW : calc vehicle, steering, info, and nav ages
CGW -> CGW : gVehicleStateAgeMs =\npickFresherAgeMs(vehicleSignalAgeMs, chassisAgeMs)
CGW -> CGW : gNavContextAgeMs =\npickFresherAgeMs(navSignalAgeMs, infoAgeMs)
CGW -> CGW : boundaryAlive = 1 only when\nchassis/body/info ages <= 300
CGW -> CGW : warningPathStatus = 0/1/2 by\nvehicle/nav/steering freshness and emergency path
CGW -> CGW : failSafeMode from warningPathStatus\nand forceFailSafe override
CGW -> CGW : routingPolicy =\n0 fail-safe / 2 emergency / 1 nominal
note right of CGW
Representative age gates
- gVehicleStateAgeMs
- gNavContextAgeMs
- gSteeringAgeMs

Representative outputs
- domainBoundaryStatus
- warningPathStatus
- routingPolicy
- failSafeMode
end note

== Boundary Publish ==

CGW -> CoreBus : CoreState::domainBoundaryStatus /\nwarningPathStatus / routingPolicy
CGW -> Consumers : fail-safe and gateway state\npublication for downstream consumers
deactivate CGW

note over Veh, Consumers
Representative runtime chain
1. Vehicle, steering, infotainment, and nav freshness converge in CGW
2. CGW computes boundaryAlive and warningPathStatus from age windows
3. CGW derives fail-safe mode and final routing policy
4. CoreState and gateway consumers receive the boundary-routing posture
end note

@enduml
